body: Can you reproduce this with a sample project? Looks like there's an issue with the `R.bool.leak_canary_watcher_watch_dismissed_dialogs` resource, but can't debug  further  without a sample project.

I try to make standalone project to reproduce this. failed. it seems normal in demo project.
Here is the infomation:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16788980/123808208-1e473d00-d923-11eb-80e1-6c117223f017.png)

I think use ApplicaionContext to load resource would be ok.
Thanks. That looks like a theming issue, which I can work around by using the app context.

repository.description: A memory leak detection library for Android.
